{"tid":2389371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中央扮無懼制裁「打腫臉充胖子」","createTime":"2021-02-01T00:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T00:40:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2c9424b949e11f31a73eeed3c4c8d4f5c4bfda66","tid":2389371,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T00:29:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/QICZTLOMPREE5KLGURABCJ5EX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FQICZTLOMPREE5KLGURABCJ5EX4%2F&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G5mjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=ef2e45ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210201%2FQICZTLOMPREE5KLGURABCJ5EX4%2F&h=8a73ddc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210201/QICZTLOMPREE5KLGURABCJ5EX4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中央扮無懼制裁「打腫臉充胖子」<br />\n<br />\n北京派「國家隊」南下，港股屢次破頂，被美國制裁的中資股亦大升。時事評論員劉銳紹分析，中共只是「打腫臉充胖子」，營造香港經濟繁榮及中企不受美制裁影響的印象，卻變相「御准」內地投資者瘋狂走資削弱經濟。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：北水基金：追捧科網股<br />\n<br />\n劉認為被制裁的中企無法在美上市勢波及內地經濟發展；因港股已A股化，內地可用國家機器操控股價，維持中企不受制裁影響的假象，增加外國投資者信心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kPzOual-vSwE2sHPckpfjnbNYxo=/3500x2334/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7JZ3NG5MUVBWBEUWRRIFD3CV3Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkPzOual-vSwE2sHPckpfjnbNYxo%3D%2F3500x2334%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7JZ3NG5MUVBWBEUWRRIFD3CV3Y.jpg&h=6ff288b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■2015年中國股災下內地股民沒精打采。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「御准」走資掏空經濟<br />\n<br />\n劉又指，近年中國嚴打走資，內地資本家及權貴調錢離開中國極難，眼見中央指示北水南下撐港股，即「御准」藉買賣股票到港走資，無形加強北水湧港。他預期這批資金在股票買賣中轉走，不知所終，內地投資者變相「攞正牌」掏空經濟。路透社則認為，港版國安法實施的敏感時刻，港股與A股一同上揚，尤以權重較大的金融股率先領漲，隱含中國「金融保衞戰」背後穩定包括港股等金融市場的良苦用心。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，內地曾多次出動國家隊救市。2015年A股在政策市催谷下兩個月暴漲四成，至6月卻急挫四成。總理李克強力主暴力救市，據悉救市方案規模達1.72萬億人民幣，加上大量行政手段禁止「惡意沽空」，集中購買藍籌股ETF。惟市場恐慌下越救越衰、越衰越沽，A股跌勢到2016年2月才告一段落，不少官員因此下馬，包括銀保監主席項俊波、中證監副主席姚剛等；A股亦從此開始了長達多年熊市。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/684LVzb8PujRTsTppwMi343-lAA=/1574x777/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AJ3YBGSPBZCN7KCNG5GIEXIJA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F684LVzb8PujRTsTppwMi343-lAA%3D%2F1574x777%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAJ3YBGSPBZCN7KCNG5GIEXIJA4.jpg&h=ed2d01b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b969171a9c2f4c5088d5c5591450089fd08b6b2","tid":2389371,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T00:40:52.000Z","msg":"支那得嗰廿年金融歷史，學人炒股？咁咪仆街囉！"}]}